---
title: Fragrant Thai Spiced Tofu Curry with courgette and carrot
description: If you're looking for a dish with a little excitement, this spicy veggie curry has it in abundance. Blended Thai spices, fluffy rice and textured tofu come together to make a perfectly balanced dish that's bursting with fun and flavour.
